# Copy this to .env.local and fill in your values.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_* variables are embedded at build time and accessible in JS.
#
# ── Local development ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# You usually do NOT need to set this in dev.
# config.ts auto-detects the right IP from the Expo Metro bundler host,
# which means physical devices + Expo Go work without any config.
#
# Only set EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL if you need to force a specific backend URL,
# e.g. pointing at a staging or production server:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api/v1
